des:
Listen to KMNO 91.7FM Mana'o Radio streaming radio and show archives on Alexa enabled devices. More information is available at www.manaoradio.com.

To play the KMNO live stream, just say:
 -"Alexa, ask KMNO to play Live".

To play a KMNO show archive, just say: "Alexa, ask KMNO to play 'A Taste Of Jazz'".
You can select from many of KMNO's show archives including:
